assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Zhejiang Construction Investment Group Co.,Ltd engages in the construction business in China. It also offers general contracting of construction projects, civil air defense, road and bridge, construction, and municipal engineering, landscape gardens, forestry engineering design, consulting, airport runway, mechanical construction, equipment installation, urban and rural planning services, engineering technology development, construction machinery manufacturing and equipment leasing, construction components production and sales, mechanical and electrical equipment, hardware tools, wholesale and import and export business of building and metal materials, chemical raw materials, computers and office automation equipment, engineering technical training and consulting business, international project contracting, export of labor equipment and materials, and property management. The company was formerly known as Dohia Group Co., Ltd and changed its name to Zhejiang Construction Investment Group Co.,Ltd in June 2021. The company was founded in 2006 and is headquartered in Hangzhou, China.
